|---|---|---|
| No security headers | 🔴 High | Add `helmet` |
| No rate limiting | 🔴 High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No global error handler | 🟠 Medium | Add error middleware |
| No CORS policy | 🟠 Medium | Add `cors` with explicit origins |
| No body size limits | 🟠 Medium | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| Timestamp in `/health` | 🟡 Low | Remove or restrict endpoint |
| No input validation | 🟡 Low (now) | Add `zod`/`joi` before adding real routes |

